===Etymology 1===
Probably from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*tV-lak||arm, hand, wing}}, especially if the {{cog|och|-}} is reconstructed with ''*l-'' ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}; {{zh-ref|Handel, 2009}}). Cognate with {{och-l|腋|[[armpit]]}}, {{cog|bo|ལག་པ||hand, arm}}, {{cog|my|လက်||hand, arm}}.

However, {{zh-ref|Baxter and Sagart (2014)}} reconstruct the {{cog|och|-}} with ''*-p'' instead of ''*-k'' because of evidence from the oracle bones, making it difficult to compare to {{cog|sit-pro|*tV-lak|*lak}}. The shift from the original version ''*ɢrəp'' to a later version ''*ɢrək'' is due to dialectal variation.

{{zh-ref|Sagart (2020)}} proposes a revised {{cog|och|-}} reconstruction ''*m-rəp'', which he compares to {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*s/b-ram||rib}}.

